reviewText: Oh 80's I miss you, but these movies help
This DVD was a gift for my Brother who is a truck driver...he needs good movies to watch when he shuts his truck down at night...He told me he likes the Blues Brothers!
This was a big hit for my husband's 75th birthday!
Classics all in one at a great price.
For those who are wondering, there are 2 discs.  Each disc has two movies on it, and as expected, the Blues Brothers movies are on one and the Fletch movies are on the other disc.
I have watch both blues brothers and was very happy with it. This dvd arrived when it was suppose to
Do you like to laugh? Try not to overdose on these 4 movies.
